RESOURCE STUDIES:
(NIAAA) National Institute on Alcohol Abuse and Alcoholism
Drinking Patterns and Their Definitions - https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6104961/
1 per day  - Moderate Alcohol Consumption
3 per day ; less than 7 per week : Low-Risk Drinking and Alcohol Use Disorder (AUD)
5 per day ; Binge Drinking
8 to 10 per day;  Extreme Binge Drinking
binge on 5-7 days within a month; Heavy Drinking


